      <title>秘鲁交易员“兴奋不已”，网红股飙升 400%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/a-meme-stock-rockets-400-as-traders-feel-the-euphoria-in-peru</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁的新钱凯港尚未产生任何收入。它甚至还没有投入运营。然而，自不到一个月前首次亮相以来，该项目少数股东的股份已飙升 400%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/a-meme-stock-rockets-400-as-traders-feel-the-euphoria-in-peru</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
